85 thruster, 135 dl, 24kg swings.
Dropped the weights a lot to get some conditioning in. Tried to just take it easy but constantly move. Felt like HR was at 90-95% the entire time so… not great. Thrusters are terrible as usual, HSP are easy as usual, overall cardio is dead as usual. At least kipping pull-ups finally feel seamless. Need to work on efficiency in thrusters, especially when paired with other shoulder stuff (holding the bar in your hands won’t get your far).
Was brave/stupid enough to do this after my main weightlifting workout — 3sec paused squats at 8RPE (265x2 tho!) + 5x3 snatches @70% + 5x2+1 c+j @70%
yeah…
